    "text": "$$\n\\text{Góc giữa } MS \\text{ và } CB \\text{ bằng góc } \\widehat{SMO}, \\cos \\widehat{SMO} = \\frac{OM}{SM} = \\frac{a}{2} : \\frac{a\\sqrt{3}}{2} = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}\n$$"
